products.title: Quadro Sahara Roman Blind
products.metadescription: Uplift any space with this snazzy design from Harlequin Additions.     Vibrant, contemporary colours work together to create a smart tile design with diagonal blurred stripes. It’s unique, modern and a lot of fun.      Happily adding pattern and colour to any room in an instant,
